@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/v1
@authToken = your_jwt_token_here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/../health

###

### Authentication & Wallet

#### Connect Wallet
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/wallet/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletAddress": "7xKXtg2CW87d97TXJSDpbD5jBkheTqA83TZRuJosgAsU",
  "signature": "sample_signature_here_would_be_much_longer_in_real_implementation",
  "message": "Sign in to SolStore"
}

###

#### Verify Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Store Management

#### Create Store
POST {{baseUrl}}/stores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "storeName": "CryptoArt Gallery",
  "storeSlug": "cryptoart-gallery",
