###

#### Get User Stores
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

#### Get Store by Slug (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores/cryptoart-gallery

###

#### Update Store
PUT {{baseUrl}}/stores/store_id_here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Store Name",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "settings": {
    "currency": "SOL",
    "language": "English",
    "timezone": "UTC",
    "theme": "dark",
    "notifications": {
      "email": true,
      "sms": false,
      "push": true
    }
  }
}

###

#### Delete Store
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/stores/store_id_here
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Product Management

#### Create Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/stores/store_id_here/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Digital Art Collection #1",
  "description": "Exclusive digital art pieces",
  "price": 2.5,
  "currency": "SOL",
  "category": "Digital Art",
  "stock": "unlimited",
  "images": ["https://example.com/image1.jpg"],
  "status": "active",
  "metadata": {
    "downloadUrl": "https://example.com/download/art1.zip",
    "fileSize": "15MB",
    "fileType": "ZIP"
  }
}

###

#### Get Store Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores/store_id_here/products?page=1&limit=20&status=active

###

#### Get Single Product
GET {{baseUrl}}/stores/store_id_here/products/product_id_here

###

#### Update Product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/stores/store_id_here/products/product_id_here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Updated Product Name",
  "price": 3.0,
  "status": "active"
}

###

#### Delete Product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/stores/store_id_here/products/product_id_here
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

